There are still some issues reported in the 0.98.4 release candidate
related to compiling and linking with OpenSSL on some Solaris and 
CentOS 5 platforms. While our tests have been successful on these platforms,
your mileage may vary. If you experience problems, contact us on the ClamAV
users list, OR:

Submit bugs here:
